TextEng: I need to ask a few questions.
Can you maybe answer questions for me?
Goodbye.
How bad the plague be in here?
What do you know about all the zombies?
I need infomation about the Beggar's Nest.
Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
Text: 이상한 소문 같은 거 들은 게 있나?

TextEng: You knows anything about walking dead guys?
Text: 걸어다니는 죽은 놈들에 대해 아는 거 있어?

TextEng: Me wants information about Beggar's Nest.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
When did they first start showing up?
I want to ask something else.
Me ask different questions.
How bad has the effect of the plague been?
Are there any safe places?
Where is there safe places?
Anything strange besides the plague and undead then?
Text: 그럼 역병과 언데드 말고도 이상한 일이 있나?

TextEng: Okay, so anything besides plague and undead?
Text: 좋아, 역병이랑 언데드 빼고 또 뭐 있어?

TextEng: What do you know about the gang?
Text: 그 갱단에 대해 뭘 알고 있지?

TextEng: What you knows about gang?
What do you know about the cult?
Text: 그 사교에 대해 뭘 알고 있지?

TextEng: What you know about cult?
Tell me about the Shining Serpent.
Tell about Shining Serpent place.
Tell me about the Helmite shrine.
Tell about Helmite shrine.
When they start not being all dead?
Anything strange happen around that time?
Text: 그 무렵 뭔가 이상한 일 없었어?

TextEng: You sees strange things around then, maybe?
Text: 그때 이상한 거 본 적 있어?

TextEng: Me gots to talk at you abouts gold.
I need to talk to you about gold.
Me just going to leave. Nevermind.
Text: 나 그냥 갈게. 신경 쓰지 마.

TextEng: Actually, I'm just going to leave now.
That okay, we just go back to other questions, okay?
Text: 괜찮아, 우리 그냥 다른 질문으로 돌아가, 응?

TextEng: Forget it. Let's just go back to my other questions.
Just little bit of gold, 50 maybe, stops accidents from happening. REAL SOON!
Text: 금화 조금만, 50개 정도만 있으면 사고 안 나. 진짜 곧!

TextEng: As little as 50 gold can prevent accidents in the home. YOUR home.
Text: 금화 50개 정도만 있으면 집안 사고를 막을 수 있어. 네 집 말이야.

TextEng: Golds will protect yous from me. That good value. Pay or die!
Text: 금화 주면 나한테서 보호받아. 좋은 거래야. 돈 내, 안 그러면 죽어!

TextEng: Gold will protect you from me. A valuable service. Pay or die!
Text: 금화가 날로부터 너를 보호해 줄 거야. 귀중한 서비스지. 돈 내, 안 그러면 죽어!
